{
  "stem": "16442.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Do you know, the people who were left in the barracks, they did not have proper clothes?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the weather started getting cold already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You'd be surprised.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even the late summer, it was cold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they didn't have proper clothes and proper shoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we were coming back from our work, we used to put on three, four, five dresses, one on top of the other.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we were-- smuggled in some lipsticks because the red stripe had to be on our back, no matter what we wore.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we would give it to the girls who didn't have.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We would take all our clothes and take their, you know, rag, go back next morning with that one rag.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And during the night, we put the red stripe on it with the lipstick.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the next day or two days later-- we couldn't do it every day.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were afraid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that's how we used to smuggle in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sometimes we smuggled dresses, sometimes shoes, socks, whatever we were able.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And many times-- most of the time, we used to smuggle food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they did not really have-- they had this horrible, horrible food, which was made-- it was a watery soup, which was made of, like, turnips.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But in Europe, they used this sort of a vegetable to feed the animals.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this was in the soup, which was almost unbelievably bad.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you would just-- had to get used to eating it and say, the only way I will survive-- if I eat the camp food.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So [SIGHS] we used to bring a little stuff here and there, a extra piece of bread, or if we-- whatever we found.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really, not by the women.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
